        <abstract> 
<p>J. H. Balfour has arranged a position for him at a <hi rend="italic">Cinchona</hi> nursery. Reluctant to take this position in part because of his experiments for CD.</p> 
            <p>Asks CD’s advice and solicits his aid in finding a better colonial position. James McNab mistreats him.</p>
